  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: [erigon/2.47.0](https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/releases/tag/v2.47.0)\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux : 41-Ubuntu\r\n\r\nConsensus Layer: Lighthouse/v4.2.0-c547a11\r\n\r\nChain/Network: ETH mainnet\r\n\r\n---\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl localhost:8545   -X POST   -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"   --data '{\"method\":\"trace_block\",\"params\":[\"0x10C3960\"],\"id\":1,\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\"}'  | jq '.result[-1].type'\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n\"type\": \"reward\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl localhost:8545   -X POST   -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"   --data '{\"method\":\"trace_block\",\"params\":[\"0x10C3960\"],\"id\":1,\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\"}'  | jq '.result[-1].type'\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n\"type\": \"call\"\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behavior\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl localhost:8545   -X POST   -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"   --data '{\"method\":\"trace_block\",\"params\":[\"0x10C3960\"],\"id\":1,\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\"}'\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\"reward\" type trace is missing. Running on an older version (Erigon/2.42.0) gives  the last trace of type \"reward\".\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/assets/107944932/8e884f99-e5cc-41bb-8b2f-859503ad5b15)",
